{"tid":2169050,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警處理證物不當 男生脫藏武器罪","createTime":"2020-08-22T07:47:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T08:26:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4c40f903d314ff2bbeca60da4cddb833c1fe47ab","tid":2169050,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T07:47:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200822/HLSGXL7XX5C6JMEBJOWBT6UHBI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200822%2FHLSGXL7XX5C6JMEBJOWBT6UHBI%2F&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6QmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=b621fad4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200822%2FHLSGXL7XX5C6JMEBJOWBT6UHBI%2F&h=2ef2b78b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200822/HLSGXL7XX5C6JMEBJOWBT6UHBI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n警處理證物不當 男生脫藏武器罪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dqI7Bf0we4wg7pcfG90YdUmuiYs=/1301x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O73RPI4IG5A27AET4QGZ72JVIQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdqI7Bf0we4wg7pcfG90YdUmuiYs%3D%2F1301x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FO73RPI4IG5A27AET4QGZ72JVIQ.jpg&h=67caea5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■今年元旦大批市民上街在港島一帶遊行。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】理工大學男生今年元旦遊行當天，在灣仔修頓球場遭防暴警追捕，事後被指背囊內藏有近百個鐵蒺藜，因而被控；惟辯方審訊時直指該背囊並非屬於被告。案件昨裁決，裁判官崔美霞指警員一度將證物放在地上，又曾徒手處理證物，未有立即將證物置於膠袋內以防干擾，其處理手法導致法庭未能確定證物是否屬於被告，裁定被告罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n涉案背囊無被告物件<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，及管有95個鐵蒺藜。崔官裁決時指，當時曾追捕被告的警署警長供稱，他拾起地上背囊時不肯定上面有否防護套。崔官指現場有多於一個背囊，加上警員未能於涉案背囊搜出被告個人物件，故法庭不能接納兩警辨認被告背包的證供。<br />\n<br />\n另外，雖然警員檢驗後證實裝有95個鐵蒺藜的紙盒上有被告的指模，惟辯方質疑警員處理鐵蒺藜的程序有問題。崔官亦指警員曾。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC28/20"},{"pid":"635e2cdc52657125753f9d7ebf543a1063a67a78","tid":2169050,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T07:49:01.000Z","msg":"勁好彩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597d0e531b88b61e4cc8b66a5ae6bcced75405fd","tid":2169050,"uid":179817,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"635e2cdc52657125753f9d7ebf543a1063a67a78","tid":2169050,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T07:49:01.000Z","msg":"勁好彩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T07:49:42.000Z","msg":"咩好彩<br />\n根本就係老屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44eda5910ca0fb9b8f1d09f080b417468dd05369","tid":2169050,"uid":79563,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T07:49:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加上警員<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">未能於涉案背囊搜出被告個人物件</span></span></strong>，故法庭不能接納兩警辨認被告背包的證供。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學習重點"},{"pid":"56781c6bf63336f536164436580ad2aefece7648","tid":2169050,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"597d0e531b88b61e4cc8b66a5ae6bcced75405fd","tid":2169050,"uid":179817,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"635e2cdc52657125753f9d7ebf543a1063a67a78","tid":2169050,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T07:49:01.000Z","msg":"勁好彩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T07:49:42.000Z","msg":"咩好彩<br />\n根本就係老屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T07:50:12.000Z","msg":"試吓遇到紅官？"},{"pid":"b27c23e49825679fa7c9eef3e06014c2021e4283","tid":2169050,"uid":16676,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T07:50:20.000Z","msg":"擺明班狗畜砌人生豬肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba06027cc249d1621818962bb19d300210babe1","tid":2169050,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":